title: The rise and fall of Skype
description: Microsoft says Skype "remains a great option." But it has lost daily users in the past three years, while other services, including Microsoft Teams, have grown.

title: Why the electric vehicle boom could put a major strain on the U.S. power grid
description: The EV revolution could put a big strain on the nation's electric grid, an aging system built for a world that runs on fossil fuels.

title: Tesla reported 466,140 deliveries for the second quarter, and production of 479,700 vehicles
description: Tesla just posted its second-quarter vehicle production and deliveries report for 2023.
